    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and still drives like a dream! It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-loved and carefully maintained, with just the usual character you\u2019d expect from a car that\u2019s actually been enjoyed. If you\u2019re looking for something dependable that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
      "price": 34500.0,
