    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine and a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox. This example boasts essential mechanical updates, including a reinforced rear subframe and a serviced VANOS system to ensure variable valve timing precision. The factory M-variable differential lock remains tight, providing superb lateral traction. Performance is bolstered by a refreshed cooling system and a suspension setup that maintains factory-spec geometry. While showing honest wear reflective of its condition, the powertrain remains a testament to BMW M engineering, offering a visceral, analog driving experience without the common failure points.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
