    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that perfectly balances performance and everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, complemented by original alloy wheels that remain free of curb rash. While there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with highway driving, the body lines are straight and free of any significant dents or scratches. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment featuring premium leather upholstery that shows only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. All onboard electronics\u2014including the high-fidelity sound system, dual-zone climate control, and navigation\u2014are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises, backed by a comprehensive service history. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a reliable, turn-key car that has been cared for with pride and is ready for its next owner to enjoy the drive.",
      "price": 34500.0,
