    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is super reliable and ready for its next adventure. Everything runs smoothly, and I\u2019ve kept up with the maintenance so you can just hop in and go. Come by and see it for yourself\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have!",
